  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into the World of Bulb – A Robot with a Spark of Determination.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>One Mistake</strong>, you take control of <strong>Bulb</strong>, a small but resolute robot powered by nothing more than a battery, a glowing light bulb, and wire-like limbs. Driven by curiosity and purpose, Bulb embarks on a mission to unravel the secrets hidden across dimensions.</p>",
